Get USPORTS wrestling athletes rankings

Source: R/wrestling_athlete_rankings.R
wrestling_athlete_rankings.Rd

Get USPORTS wrestling athletes rankings

Usage

wrestling_athlete_rankings(gender, weight)

Arguments

gender

Gender of athletes "m" or "w"

weight

weight class

Value

A tibble.

Examples

wrestling_athlete_rankings("m",90)
#> # A tibble: 65 × 5
#>    Weight.Category  Rank Name             School        Last.Updated
